{"tid":417981,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【國教重臨】要求挑選愛國歌曲「最感動歌詞」 聖保羅書院小學否認推國教","createTime":"2017-09-29T07:25:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-18T11:33:49.000Z","uid":83569,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"41a84ee16b1e0efbc57422c95a0d19e716082ddf","tid":417981,"uid":83569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T07:25:38.000Z","msg":"直資名校聖保羅書院小學製作的校本輔導教材《情繫祖國》，被家長質疑灌輸愛國情感。有家長向時事評論員林忌報料，指老師近日要求學生完成一張「聽歌想國情」工作紙，提供中華人民共和國國歌《義勇軍進行曲》、《歌唱祖國》、《龍的傳人》等8首愛國歌曲，要求學生聆聽後寫下「最能感動我的歌詞」。校方指「情繫祖國」只是校本輔導主題之一，否認推行國教。<br />\n<br />\n人大常委本月初通過《國歌法》，明文規定將國歌重點納入中小學愛國教育，料將納入香港基本法，備受外界爭議。林忌向《蘋果》表示，上述家長向他稱近日檢查兒子功課時發現上述工作紙。家長按工作紙指示登上內聯網查閱歌曲清單，發現全為愛國歌曲，包括《義勇軍進行曲》、劉德華的《中國人》、李健復的《龍的傳人》等。不過，該家長形容老師「係咁意派畀小朋友做」，沒有特別指導如何作答，因此縱覺得工作紙有問題，亦唯有『在家中反洗腦』，兒子最終「是旦做咗（工作紙）就算」。<br />\n<br />\n根據家長提供的資料，教材列出8首歌曲，要求學生選擇聽其中1首，回答「最能感動我的歌詞」，及會把歌曲推薦給誰人聽、原因為何，最後一題則要求學生為歌曲設計CD封套。該8首歌曲為：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170929&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=57268722\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170929%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D57268722&d=hz2uHQdD25P5LPti95DZtP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=ed9c844d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170929%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D57268722&h=4f80a1ba\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170929&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=57268722</a><br />\n要求挑選愛國歌曲「最感動歌詞」 聖保羅書院小學否認推國教"},{"pid":"f1569790f944d2f1ee655a2b2e4e8da43e3bbd70","tid":417981,"uid":83569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T07:32:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"74980fdaabc25c91826ce44aa98c275c36c4c0fc","tid":417981,"uid":136773,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T07:36:48.000Z","msg":"應該加埋 beyond-大地 beyond-長城 同埋王傑-誰明浪子心上去比人選"},{"pid":"7f5a2287a50f91e2c038290000354430b8101e9e","tid":417981,"uid":3180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T07:40:08.000Z","msg":"把我們的血肉，築成我們新的長城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n13億夠唔夠起過條新長城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a26ef51479328a8e388666449b7c76ae3016a6c","tid":417981,"uid":14792,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T07:46:33.000Z","msg":"聖保羅但愛國 不如改名做毛澤東中學啦 屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9bda5a768b476e768c955b9a647e4224f18f68f","tid":417981,"uid":83569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T10:46:13.000Z","msg":"推佢間垃圾名校"},{"pid":"fb9a03cb6e50e411902ccbbf2effc7e45fb48473","tid":417981,"uid":83569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T10:59:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"183ee6f68c3f8c41622ed7278e8b228fd1e263be","tid":417981,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T11:05:59.000Z","msg":"真愛是真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b237620cdb00c119273eb196df2e2919434d00c5","tid":417981,"uid":83569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T09:04:30.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f32c82686bc1f66458d73d57d49c19ef231556bb","tid":417981,"uid":83569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T11:33:49.000Z","msg":"推一推 多一個人睇到topic 都好"}]}